SB 101 Engrossed 2026 Regular Session Abraham
Designates a portion of Louisiana Highway 384 in Cameron Parish as the "Daniel Edward
Didelot Memorial Highway".
Directs DOTD to erect and maintain appropriate signs of this designation provided certain
cost restrictions are satisfied.
Effective August 1, 2026.
